WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:13.280
Ingredients:
- 1 Cabbage (1.5 kg), 2 medium beets
- 7 cloves of garlic
- 0.5 cups of vegetable oil
- 1 cup of vinegar, 3/4 cup sugar
- 2 tbsp. l. salt, 1 L of water
- Bay leaf, Allspice (peas)

00:00:40.700 --> 00:01:10.200
- Cut the cabbage, 
so to get the "petals" of 3 cm

00:01:54.200 --> 00:02:04.200
- garlic cut into plates 
and put in a bowl with cabbage

00:02:10.200 --> 00:02:25.200
- beets cut into strips

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:55.200
- Pour the oil, vinegar

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:49.200
- boil the marinade
  (water, salt, sugar, spices)

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:16.200
- after boil, pour into cabbage

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:44.200
- put the press

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:54.200
- cabbage ready for the next day

00:04:58.200 --> 00:05:04.000
Bon Appetit!

